s\n- 2 XXL Premium Stickers\n- Unique Collector's Box", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 18, "name": "Science fiction"}, {"id": 20, "name": "Thriller"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/beyond-a-steel-sky-utopia-edition", "videos": [{"id": 55893, "name": "Release Date Trailer", "video_id": "lR7ffBQHTGw"}]}